# .dockerignore
#
# The Dockerfile in this repo is intentionally a thin reference/extension
# file. The real image is produced by `nix build` + `docker load`.
#
# Nothing from the build context is copied into the production image layers.
# We keep the ignore list strict for hygiene in case someone points
# a registry automated build or `docker buildx` at the directory.

*
!Dockerfile
!README.md
!docker-compose.yml

# Even if we did COPY things in a variant stage, we would not want these:
.git
.gitignore
flake.lock
flake.nix
Makefile
result
result-*
.direnv
